def getClassifyModels(models: list[str]):
    grouped = defaultdict(lambda: defaultdict(list))
    for model in models:
        model_id = model["id"]
        owner = model.get("owned_by", "unknown")
        category = classify_model(model_id)
        grouped[category][owner].append(model_id)
    return grouped
